OL,3,CDame Sarah Mullally to be installed as
OL,4,Cfirst female Archbishop of Canterbury
OL,6,FDame Sarah Mullally will be installed
OL,7,Fas the first female Archbishop of
OL,8,FCanterbury on Wednesday.
OL,10,FDame Sarah legally became Archbishop
OL,11,Fin January but will now be enthroned
OL,12,Fat an installation ceremony at
OL,13,FCanterbury Cathedral.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G1/7
