OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F413A1774436769
OL,3,CDame Sarah Mullally to be installed as
OL,4,Cfirst female Archbishop of Canterbury
OL,6,FThe Archbishop will deliver her first
OL,7,Fsermon in the role to a congregation
OL,8,Fincluding the Prince and Princess of
OL,9,FWales, representing the King, Prime
OL,10,FMinister Sir Keir Starmer,
OL,11,FConservative Party leader Kemi
OL,12,FBadenoch, faith leaders, charity
OL,13,Frepresentatives, and schoolchildren.
OL,15,FThe service will not involve holy
OL,16,Fcommunion, but those gathered may
OL,17,Fexchange handshakes as is traditional
OL,18,Fin offering a sign of peace to those
OL,19,Fnearby.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G2/7
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
