PN,41303
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F413A1774436769
OL,3,CDame Sarah Mullally to be installed as
OL,4,Cfirst female Archbishop of Canterbury
OL,6,FThe congregation will include more
OL,7,Fthan two dozen primates from the
OL,8,FAnglican Communion ` Christian
OL,9,Fchurches around the world of which
OL,10,FDame Sarah is now the spiritual leader.
OL,12,FAmong them will be some of the first
OL,13,Ffemale Anglican bishops from across
OL,14,FAfrica, who will join a procession
OL,15,Fthrough the Cathedral.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G3/7
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
