PN,41304
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F413A1774436769
OL,3,CDame Sarah Mullally to be installed as
OL,4,Cfirst female Archbishop of Canterbury
OL,6,FThe Pope will not attend but will send
OL,7,Fa representative from the Holy See,
OL,8,Fand the new Archbishop of Westminster,
OL,9,Fwho is the leader of Catholics in
OL,10,FEngland and Wales, will give a reading
OL,11,Ffrom the Old Testament.
OL,13,FDame Sarah will become the first
OL,14,Ffemale to hold the high office of
OL,15,FArchbishop of Canterbury in its 1,400-
OL,16,Fyear history.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G4/7
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
