PN,41305
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F413A1774436769
OL,3,CDame Sarah Mullally to be installed as
OL,4,Cfirst female Archbishop of Canterbury
OL,6,FShe arrived in the city on Sunday at
OL,7,Fthe end of a six-day walking
OL,8,Fpilgrimage from London, telling those
OL,9,Fshe greeted that she was "very
OL,10,Frelieved" to complete the 87-mile
OL,11,Ftrek, which had been "a real joy" to
OL,12,Fundertake.
OL,14,FDame Sarah, who was chief nursing
OL,15,Fofficer in England before she was
OL,16,Fordained, has also invited NHS nurses
OL,17,Fand carers working in hospitals and
OL,18,Fhospices in Canterbury to attend the
OL,19,Fceremony.
OL,26,@qD@ZOUrD@IO]sD@VOUsD@aO]
