PN,41306
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F413A1774436769
OL,3,CDame Sarah Mullally to be installed as
OL,4,Cfirst female Archbishop of Canterbury
OL,6,FMr Monteith previously said the
OL,7,Finstallation of the first female
OL,8,FArchbishop "would have almost been
OL,9,Funimaginable even 50 years ago".
OL,11,FHe added: "As we combine centuries of
OL,12,Ftradition in this ancient service with
OL,13,Fthose elements unique to Sarah's
OL,14,Fministry, we welcome her to our
OL,15,FCathedral and diocese, and pray for
OL,16,Fher as she takes on the role of
OL,17,FArchbishop of Canterbury."
OL,26,@pD@LOUqD@_O]sD@KOUyD@ZO]
